# AKOS — External Adviser Engagement (ADVOPS plane)

Use this rule for any change that touches the **External Adviser Engagement plane** — the cross-program scaffolding for Legal, Fiscal, IP, Banking, Certification, and Notary advisers (workstream `hol_opera_ws_5`). Complements [`akos-holistika-operations.mdc`](akos-holistika-operations.mdc) (MasterData / Supabase) and [`akos-governance-remediation.mdc`](akos-governance-remediation.mdc) (HLK asset class), and inherits planning traceability from [`akos-planning-traceability.mdc`](akos-planning-traceability.mdc).

## Plane summary

| Plane | Owns | System of record |
|-------|------|------------------|
| **MKTOPS** ([Initiative 14](../../docs/wip/planning/14-holistika-internal-gtm-mops/master-roadmap.md)) | Funnel, qualification, lead intake | `holistika_gtm_*` rows + `holistika_ops.lead_intake` |
| **FINOPS** ([Initiative 18](../../docs/wip/planning/18-hlk-finops-counterparty-stripe/master-roadmap.md)) | Counterparty metadata; ledger gates | `FINOPS_COUNTERPARTY_REGISTER.csv` + mirror; `finops.*` (Postgres) |
| **OPS / PMO** | Program portfolio, stakeholder index | `process_list.csv` + `TOPIC_PMO_CLIENT_DELIVERY_HUB.md` |
| **TECHOPS / DEVOPS** | Component matrix, infra, migrations | `COMPONENT_SERVICE_MATRIX.csv` + `supabase/migrations/` |
| **ADVOPS** (this plane) | External adviser engagement, per discipline | `ADVISER_ENGAGEMENT_DISCIPLINES.csv` + open-questions / filed-instruments registers + GOI/POI |

## Knowledge dimension: GOI/POI

`GOI_POI_REGISTER.csv` (Initiative 21 / P1) is a **canonical knowledge dimension**: every private organisation or person referenced from the vault, ADVOPS registers, transcripts, or KM manifests is captured by `ref_id` (`POI-<DISC>-<SLUG>-<YYYY>` / `GOI-<DISC>-<SLUG>-<YYYY>`). Documents reference `ref_id`s only; obfuscation is deterministic. Identity mapping (real name ↔ ref_id) is **off-repo** and operator-managed (see [`SOP-HLK_GOIPOI_REGISTER_MAINTENANCE_001`](../../docs/references/hlk/v3.0/Admin/O5-1/People/Compliance/SOP-HLK_GOIPOI_REGISTER_MAINTENANCE_001.md)).

## Discipline routing

`ADVISER_ENGAGEMENT_DISCIPLINES.csv` is the **lookup** that drives:

- **Per-discipline sections** of [`EXTERNAL_COUNSEL_HANDOFF_PACKAGE.md`](../../docs/references/hlk/v3.0/Admin/O5-1/People/Legal/EXTERNAL_COUNSEL_HANDOFF_PACKAGE.md).
- **Filtering** in [`scripts/export_adviser_handoff.py`](../../scripts/export_adviser_handoff.py) (Initiative 21 / P7).
- **`canonical_role` / `default_process_item_id`** when adding a new question, instrument, or POI/GOI — pre-fill from the discipline row instead of typing them per question.

Adding a discipline (e.g. accounting, employment, regulatory affairs) is a **row-level change** to the lookup CSV plus an optional new POI/GOI rows; **no schema migrations** required.

## Forward-only privacy posture (D-CH-2)

- **Current tip is redacted** via [`scripts/redact_transcripts_p2.py`](../../scripts/redact_transcripts_p2.py) and [`SOP-HLK_TRANSCRIPT_REDACTION_001`](../../docs/references/hlk/v3.0/Admin/O5-1/People/Compliance/SOP-HLK_TRANSCRIPT_REDACTION_001.md).
- **Commit history rewriting (`git filter-repo`) is deferred.** Re-evaluation triggers in [`docs/wip/planning/21-hlk-adviser-engagement-and-goipoi/decision-log.md`](../../docs/wip/planning/21-hlk-adviser-engagement-and-goipoi/decision-log.md) (D-CH-2).
- **Never** add a new transcript or call note that contains real names; substitute first.

## When to use this rule

- Any new or updated row in `GOI_POI_REGISTER.csv`, `ADVISER_ENGAGEMENT_DISCIPLINES.csv`, `ADVISER_OPEN_QUESTIONS.csv`, `FOUNDER_FILED_INSTRUMENTS.csv`.
- Any change to the counsel handoff package or its per-discipline sections.
- Any new transcript or redaction action under `delete-legal-transcripts/`.
- New ADVOPS-related processes or workstreams in `process_list.csv` (`hol_opera_ws_5`, `hol_opera_dtp_31x`).
- Mirror DDL or sync changes for `compliance.goipoi_register_mirror`, `compliance.adviser_engagement_disciplines_mirror`, `compliance.adviser_open_questions_mirror`, `compliance.founder_filed_instruments_mirror`.

## Required runbook

1. **Update CSVs first** (`GOI_POI_REGISTER`, `ADVISER_ENGAGEMENT_DISCIPLINES`, `ADVISER_OPEN_QUESTIONS`, `FOUNDER_FILED_INSTRUMENTS`).
2. **Validate**: `py scripts/validate_hlk.py` (PASS gate); `py scripts/validate_hlk_vault_links.py`.
3. **Update vault MD** (handoff package, per-discipline sections, fact pattern, open-questions human view, filed-instruments human view) — these are derived views.
4. **Sync mirrors** (operator gate): `py scripts/sync_compliance_mirrors_from_csv.py --goipoi-register-only` etc., review output, apply via Supabase MCP `service_role`.
5. **Update process_list.csv** only via operator-approved tranche per [`akos-governance-remediation.mdc`](akos-governance-remediation.mdc); never mutate without a row in the initiative `decision-log.md`.

